                        <h6 class="before-label">BEFORE</h6>
                        <h6 class="after-label">AFTER</h6>
                        <h5>The Solution</h5>
                        <p>From 2009-2016, ATP provided mainly fruit trees for beautifying the school grounds:
                            apple, apricot, sour cherry, mulberry, pear, peach, jujube and almond.
                        </p>
                        <h5>The Outcome</h5>
                        <p>The school gardener sells the harvest and the profits go toward school supplies and more.
                            School staff and students are active in planting activities, and children play games in the shade while
                            older students pick fruit. The schoolyard has become a place where youth gather all year.
                        </p>
